				<p class="postmetadata">30.04.2014 (Norbert Rost) Kategorie: <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/category/die-kleinen-schritte/" title="Alle Beiträge in Die kleinen Schritte ansehen" rel="category tag">Die kleinen Schritte</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/category/pressemitteilung-2/" title="Alle Beiträge in Pressemitteilung ansehen" rel="category tag">Pressemitteilung</a>  &middot; Tags: <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/christoph-senz/" rel="tag">Christoph Senz</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/dieter-janecek/" rel="tag">Dieter Janecek</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/muenchen/" rel="tag">München</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/paul-nellen/" rel="tag">Paul Nellen</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/peak-oil/" rel="tag">peak oil</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/werner-zittel/" rel="tag">Werner Zittel</a>  &middot; <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/2014/04/veranstaltung-peak-oil-muenchen/#comments" title="Kommentiere Veranstaltung: Peak Oil in M&#252;nchen (+Hamburg)">31 Kommentare &#187;</a> </p>

